                    <h1>NAVIGATION</h1>
                    <h2>Location</h2>
                    <p>There will be one primary navigation bar located across the top of webpage directly underneath the logo. It will be center aligned with numerous links to click on that will take you to other pages on the website. The pages will be as follows: Home, About, Media, Learn, and Contact.</p>
                    <h2>Size</h2>
                    <p>The nav bar will be the same width as the banner with the logo that it is placed beneath, but the height will be much smaller, about 25px in height.</p>
                    <h2>Effects</h2>
                    <p>When the computer cursor is hovering over the link, the color of the link will change. Iâ€™m not sure if I want the background to change color or the text to change color, but there will be contrast to further indicate this page is a link.</p>
